- Spanning GPU memory bandwidth optimization, KV cache management, batching strategies, and multi-GPU inference, the book delivers insights forged in real- world production.
- Chris brings clarity to complex topics like Nsight profiling, transformer attention tuning, and distributed scaling, making it a must-read for performance engineers bridging hardware, systems, and AI. —Amer Ather, cloud and ML performance engineer at Netflix The most comprehensive and up-to-date guide on building modern-day AI systems.
