- Chris’s latest book is packed full of content that helps me in my day-to-day activities of optimizing and tuning AI workloads.
- He covers all of today’s AI systems performance issues—and provides solutions that are invaluable to every company trying to put AI into production. —Antje Barth, member of technical staff at Amazon AGI There is no other book in this field that even comes close to AI Systems Performance Engineering.
